\h BARS \d

\uUSAGE\n
!bars \s[\dhp mp pp fp\s]\d

\uDESCRIPTION\n
Display one or more status bars.
When no arguments are provided, you'll see 4 status bars illustrating your remaining HP, MP, PP, and FP.
To indicate which status bars you would like to see, you may provide any combination of the following arguments:
"hp", "mp", "pp", and "fp"

\uEXAMPLES\n
\qbars\d to see all 4 status bars.4`
\qbars hp\d to see a status bar representing your hit points.4`
\qbars hp mp\d to see status bars representing your hit points and magic points.4`

\uSEE ALSO\n
feeling, stats
